InMobi,is,the,world,s,largest,independent,mobile,advertising,network,Publishers,use,the,network,to,monetize,their,inventory,while,advertisers,use,it,to,reach,their,audience,The,InMobi,API,allows,developers,to,insert,their,ads,in,J,ME,PSP,or,any,other,platform,With,the,API,users,can,manage,multiple,platforms,The,API,can,also,be,used,to,integrate,mobile,websites,iOS,Android,apps,and,other,mobile,applications,It,uses,HTTP,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML